description: LMK Group AB engages in the manufacturing perishable prepared foods. The company is headquartered in Spanga, Stockholm and currently employs 413 full-time employees.  The firm operates as a supplier of meal kits in the Nordic region. The firm operates in Sweden, Norway and Denmark under the brands Linas Matkasse, Godtlevert, Adams Matkasse and RetNemt.
name: LMK Group AB (publ)
